It's easy to pocket carry and just disappears in your pocket or purse.  It’s identical in size to the Ruger LCP but feels a bit softer to shoot than the LCP.The full package for each TCP comes with everything that came with the gun from the factory: original box (matching serial number), Taurus locking system with key, all paperwork, and the 6-round magazine supplied by Taurus.  I’ve also included an extra factory mag that I had purchased (first buyer gets it), plus I’ve added a Talon Grip to the TCP we’ve shot for increased control and comfort.
